    Interface Description
    NearflyClientTarget  
    NearflyListener
    Interface which is needed to react to concerns of the nearfly service
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    A set of constants used within the app.
    NearflyBindingActivity
    Helps the integration of NearflyService, manages the binding of the NearflyService and queries the necessary permissions at the beginning of the activity if necessary.
    NearflyClient
    A Bound Service that wrap up the feature functions from the Google Nearby API and MQTT Paho.
    NearflyClient.State
    Helps to interpret the NearflyListener.onLogMessage(String) correctly NearflyClient.State.CONNECTED: Was successfully connected.
    NearflyService
    A Bound Service that wrap up the feature functions from the Google Nearby API and MQTT Paho.
